Description: Stroll the beautiful streets of Rosebud, visiting shops and unique vendors!  Autumn at its best!

Gerald City Park:  12:00 pm - Gates open, 1:00 pm - Josh Wuerfful, 2:30 pm - Pam Setser, 4:30 pm - The Malpass Borthers, 6:30 pm - The Amanda Cook Band.  All ticket, food, and drink proceeds to benefit the extension of the Rock Island Trail from Gerald to Rosebud.
